I'll wait for KSL to post with Jaws before posting about him.

::Zardus::

Zardus looks at Lambda. "Hmm.. Well, I would like to know about your 
past first, and any skills you have."

He recieves Punch's transmission, replying to it silently. "Hmm.. It 
would take them quite a long time to repair the Ark," the 
transmission reads, "And it won't do them much good. It would be best 
not to attack them right now though. We might soon need to manuever 
them to attack the Predacons, and it would be hard to do while we are 
attacking them."
